<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>탐스럽다 [탐스럽따]</dt><br>
<dd>desirable; appetizing; coveted</dd><br>
<dd>마음이 몹시 끌리도록 보기에 좋은 데가 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Good-looking enough to attract one's mind.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>바람직하다 [바람지카다]</dt><br>
